{"tid":1301461,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【DQ洗咩講理由】香港人返到國內被賣港賊DQ，請一齊聲討賣港賊","createTime":"2019-07-09T15:52:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T01:49:20.000Z","uid":264655,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"03d5bcf709ef2608217c12047c2e07e3459e3506","tid":1301461,"uid":264655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T15:52:05.000Z","msg":"PRD珠三角壁球比賽已舉了十多年，有廣州，澳門，香港，台灣，北京，上海等多個地方的球參與，而今年2019 的比賽在7月6至7日兩天，在廣州亞運體育館舉行。<br />\n<br />\n多年來，PRD壁球比賽核心籌委旨在提供平台，予各地球員能交流球技，提升壁球在各地的普及程度，大受各地壁球愛好者歡迎。<br />\n<br />\n今年由廣州某某球會 (見圖) 主辦，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大會重金禮聘香港國際球證 ANDREW HO (HUIN CHOONG)</span></strong>做球證，身為國際專業球證，竟然在準決賽無理DQ香港The Squash Club 男子隊，取消整隊4名球員的參賽資格，各地球會即時一同向大會及ANDREW HO (HUIN CHOONG) 反映裁判不公，無理， 但香港國際球證ANDREW HO (HUIN CHOONG)只回應 &quot;<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不需要跟你們解釋</span></strong>&quot;， 令一眾參賽者嘩然。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>及後更在社交媒體抹黑球員打假波！實在是無中生有！顛倒是非！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1S7VEkU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1S7VEkU.jpg&h=9cfeac76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>請問！！</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">第一天初賽，TSC 男子隊計細分其實是首名出線，何來打假波？如果佢覺得首名出線都是打假波，為何初賽當天不立即DQ？要到第二天準決賽開始前才DQ香港隊？ 還是佢根本自己没有第一天參與賽事，其後任意DQ球員？？<br />\n<br />\n第二天準決賽，TSC 男子隊，連波都無打過，打咩假波？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">各地參賽球會，為了向大會反映不滿不公不正的裁判，即時一同離場，炋葛賽事！</span></span>]<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[b]<span style=\"color: blue;\">香港國際球證ANDREW HO (HUIN CHOONG) - 紅衫人</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DkbGz4G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDkbGz4G.jpg&h=6e65184f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>其他地區參賽者在社交媒體一同聲討不公平的裁判</strong></span></span><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vVK1zUe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvVK1zUe.jpg&h=07cc9c12&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3e66dca34ecc120d4d97d1e1bced8054f19946d1","tid":1301461,"uid":264123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:54:51.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"},{"pid":"023d7f3db57aa083bf6a04bdeae05b09e6a9999e","tid":1301461,"uid":8938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:58:12.000Z","msg":"返到國內<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eabe65e913b1f99b603f8eb7ac0aaf69f8f83d9","tid":1301461,"uid":264123,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T17:02:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qfcVEW1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqfcVEW1.png&h=1955f151&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n壁球界 專出藍絲？"},{"pid":"63c23810da1a577b752d7e3f77e6b6dd391b9e0b","tid":1301461,"uid":264655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T17:18:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1fc4792ea368e8092847067757001b52222d13db","tid":1301461,"uid":266111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T08:45:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"698f98d08c429918e9b4032471de990f8d28b969","tid":1301461,"uid":264123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T16:18:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c11ff4956cb447f80a599f4aafdb542179aeee63","tid":1301461,"uid":264655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T17:06:43.000Z","msg":"我推完又推"},{"pid":"d9eb2f34e921576cd4d7e66a89c804fdbdcf8890","tid":1301461,"uid":264123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T01:47:19.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"3db8aa80abbd13d2a261c6961504ef964212dca1","tid":1301461,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T01:49:20.000Z","msg":"去到你個國內就預左黑暗架啦"}]}